Wonderful program, Thank you Sheila6
Will seed till i run out of traffic. This one is a must-see for all beginning and self-taught composers out there.

Actually I didn't expect much as this is quite an intangible subject. But I must say Goodall has been doing his homework and does present the material very well, indeed! Bits from classical to down-south early blue notes blues to illustrate the bits & pieces that constitutes music.

In short: Thumbs up for this!

Thanks for sharing.

Will seed.
Namaste, sheila6. Quite the eclectic material you present. Hope this dloads better than Albinoni Concerto torrent. It looks so gooood.

What a useful series.
